s-tile__animated box-border"><!--[--><!----><div class="grid-container-item min-w-0 col-full ins-tile__image"><!--[--><div style="background-color:rgba(2, 2, 2, 255);" class="ins-tile__picture"><picture class="ins-picture ins-picture--full"><!--[--><source srcset="https://dfvc2y3mjtc8v.cloudfront.net/108682511/call-to-action-6VPvob/mNrz0Wg-2000x2000.webp, https://dfvc2y3mjtc8v.cloudfront.net/108682511/call-to-action-6VPvob/mNrz0Wg-2000x2000.webp 2x" media="(min-width: 900px)" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://dfvc2y3mjtc8v.cloudfront.net/108682511/call-to-action-6VPvob/mNrz0Wg-1200x1200.webp, https://dfvc2y3mjtc8v.cloudfront.net/108682511/call-to-action-6VPvob/mNrz0Wg-2000x2000.webp 2x" media="(min-width: 500px)" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://dfvc2y3mjtc8v.cloudfront.net/108682511/call-to-action-6VPvob/mNrz0Wg-600x600.webp, https://dfvc2y3mjtc8v.cloudfront.net/108682511/call-to-action-6VPvob/mNrz0Wg-1200x1200.webp 2x" type="image/webp"><!--]--><!--[--><source srcset="https://dfvc2y3mjtc8v.cloudfront.net/108682511/call-to-action-6VPvob/mNrz0Wg-2000x2000.jpg, https://dfvc2y3mjtc8v.cloudfront.net/108682511/call-to-action-6VPvob/mNrz0Wg-2000x2000.jpg 2x" media="(min-width: 900px)"><source srcset="https://dfvc2y3mjtc8v.cloudfront.net/108682511/call-to-action-6VPvob/mNrz0Wg-1200x1200.jpg, https://dfvc2y3mjtc8v.cloudfront.net/108682511/call-to-action-6VPvob/mNrz0Wg-2000x2000.jpg 2x" media="(min-width: 500px)"><source srcset="https://dfvc2y3mjtc8v.cloudfront.net/108682511/call-to-action-6VPvob/mNrz0Wg-600x600.jpg, https://dfvc2y3mjtc8v.cloudfront.net/108682511/call-to-action-6VPvob/mNrz0Wg-1200x1200.jpg 2x"><!--]--><img src="https://dfvc2y3mjtc8v.cloudfront.net/108682511/call-to-action-6VPvob/mNrz0Wg-200x200.jpg" alt="" fetchpriority="high" onload=""></picture><!----></div><!--]--></div><div class="grid-container-item min-w-0 col-content legacy_l:col-span-13 legacy_l:col-start-2 ins-tile__body"><!--[--><div class="ins-tile__body-inner"><!----><div role="heading" aria-level="2" class="ins-tile__description ins-tile__format">CALMING EFFECT Co is a Manila-based lifestyle brand powered by CE Studios® founded in 2020 by Filipino entrepreneur BigGlory Mane professionally known as BGM.

The name of the brand was inspired by his late 2019 beat tape, which reflected his story, and also by the drug "Valium".

At that time he was known as "OSTYNAGD777" for producing beats to artists such as O Side Mafia, Astro and Paul Cassimir of Owfuck and many more 

Later on, he switched his name into "BigGlory Mane" becoming the creative director and sold the company to someone behind the scenes.

Over time, the pie grew bigger as he expected. Now, the rest is History.</div><!----></div><!--]--></div><!--]--></div></div><!--[--><!--]--><!--[--><!--]--><!--[--><!--]--><!--]--></section><section class="section__wrapper w-full ins-tile ins-tile--category-products ins-tile--classic ins-tile--with-grid-settings ins-tile--with-system-settings ins-tile--with-corner-radius" id="tile-category-products-BkYTm7" tile-type="CATEGORY_PRODUCTS"><!--[--><!--[--><style> /* Roboto Mono font */ </style><style> /* Roboto Mono font */ </style><style> /* Roboto Mono font */ </style><style> /* Roboto Mono font */ </style><style> /* Roboto Mono font */ </style><style> /* Roboto Mono font */ </style><!--]--><!--]--><!--[--><style>#tile-category-products-BkYTm7 {--background-color: oklch(0 0 0);--bg-color: var(--ewp-color-a);--bg-marker-1-color: var(--ewp-color-b);--bg-marker-2-color: var(--ewp-color-c);--bg-neutral-color: var(--ewp-color-a);--bg-overlay-color: var(--ewp-color-c);--button-color: oklch(0.21342 0 0);--container-bg-color: var(--ewp-color-b);--container-fg-accented-color: var(--ewp-color-d);--container-fg-color: var(--ewp-color-f);--container-fg-muted-color: var(--ewp-color-e);--fg-accented-color: var(--ewp-color-d);--fg-color: var(--ewp-color-f);--fg-marker-1-color: var(--ewp-color-d);--fg-marker-2-color: var(--ewp-color-e);--fg-marker-3-color: var(--ewp-color-f);--fg-muted-color: var(--ewp-color-e);--fg-neutral-color: var(--ewp-color-f);--n-button-font-family: Roboto Mono, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Roboto&quot;, &quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;--n-product-name-font-family: Roboto Mono, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Roboto&quot;, &quot;Arial&quot;, sans-serif;--n-product-name-font-size: var(--responsive-font-size-12);--n-product-name-font-style: normal;--n-product-name-font-weight: 400;--n-product-name-line-height: var(--responsive-line-height-12);--n-product-price-font-family: Roboto Mono, system-ui, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Roboto&quot;, &quot;Ar